Package cs113.calendar.guiview

Class Summary
AdminArea AdminArea lets the user create and delete users.

CalendarArea This is the heart of the calendar.
FeedbackComponent Provides errors and warnings to the user.
GuiView Solitary window in the application used for all input and output.
LabeledTextField Standard JTextField with a prompt super-imposed over the control in lieu of a standard JLabel.
ListArea This is used to display the results of a search.
ListPanel Displays items in a list-like container with scroll bars.
LoginComponent Allows a user to graphically log in or logout using a simple set of text controls and buttons.
MainArea Wrapper to contain CalendarArea, ListArea, and AdminArea.

StateSelectionComponent Graphical component that consists of horizontal row of buttons, each of which represents a discrete state.
ViewState Singleton object used to represent the global state of the GUI.
